WEBVTT

00:00.408 --> 00:03.917
Earlier this year, we became owners of a football club in Wrexham.

00:05.256 --> 00:06.483
Do you feel like you know what you're doing?

00:06.685 --> 00:07.393
Absolutely not.

00:08.433 --> 00:10.172
Football means everything to people in this town.

00:11.414 --> 00:13.149
It's not life and death, it's more important than that.

00:14.519 --> 00:16.988
The team becomes an extension of the city.

00:17.434 --> 00:20.579
The hype is massive, and the town desperately needs it.

00:22.062 --> 00:23.489
This is a fun game.

